      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that won't break the bank? This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it's mechanically functional and gets you where you need to go reliably every day! You'll notice some wear and tear both inside and out that's consistent with its age and use, and it may have a few minor issues that a budget-conscious buyer can easily manage. If you're after solid transportation with room to add your own touch, this could be a great fit!",
