    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Dependable & Ready to Roll \u2014 A Great Good-Condition Pick! \ud83d\ude97 This vehicle is in good condition and delivers the kind of reliable, everyday performance you can count on! It shows the normal, expected signs of use \u2014 think minor cosmetic wear and the occasional small scuff \u2014 but nothing that gets in the way of a smooth, enjoyable drive. The interior is well-maintained and comfortable, and the mechanicals are in solid working order. If you're looking for a honest, road-ready car without paying mint-condition prices, this one deserves a serious look! \ud83d\udd11",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in fair condition, and we want to give you a complete and honest picture before you consider making a purchase. The exterior shows noticeable wear \u2014 you can expect several scratches, some paint fading, and a few minor dents that are visible upon close inspection. The interior has seen regular use: the upholstery shows wear marks and there are some scuffs on the trim panels. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it is not without its quirks \u2014 you should budget for some maintenance or repairs in the near term. This is an honest, straightforward offering for a buyer who wants reliable basic transportation and understands they are purchasing a vehicle that will need some attention. No surprises \u2014 what you see is what you get, and we encourage an independent inspection before purchase.",
      "price": 17500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in good condition, and we want to give you a clear and honest picture of what to expect. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains a decent shine and holds up nicely from a distance, though up close you'll notice some minor scratches and light wear consistent with regular daily use. There are no major dents or structural concerns, but this is not a showroom-perfect vehicle. The interior is clean and functional, with normal wear on the seats and trim \u2014 nothing that detracts from comfort or usability. Mechanically, the car runs reliably and has been maintained adequately; it's ready for everyday driving without immediate repair concerns. This is a solid, honest vehicle for a buyer who wants dependable transportation at a fair price, without paying a premium for cosmetic perfection.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Honest Deal on a Budget Runner \u2014 Priced for What It Is! \u2014 Need basic transportation without breaking the bank? This vehicle is honestly priced to reflect its current poor condition \u2014 it has visible wear, some mechanical issues that will need attention, and is best suited for a handy buyer or someone looking for an affordable project. What you see is what you get, and the price reflects exactly that! Great opportunity for a DIY mechanic or anyone who just needs something to get from A to B while they save up. Come take a look \u2014 no surprises, just straight talk and a fair deal! \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f",
      "price": 6000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
