      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in good condition, and prospective buyers can expect a reliable, well-maintained option that shows normal signs of use but remains in solid overall shape. The exterior presents with minor cosmetic wear consistent with regular driving \u2014 small scuffs or light scratches may be visible upon close inspection, but there is no significant body damage. Mechanically, the car runs well with no major issues; routine maintenance has been kept up, and the engine, transmission, and key systems are functioning properly. The interior is clean and comfortable, with upholstery showing modest wear but no tears or major stains. All primary features and electronics are in working order. This is a dependable everyday vehicle that has been cared for and is ready for its next owner without requiring immediate repairs.",
